<h1 id="oaxaca-ruby-user-group-website">Oaxaca Ruby User Group Website</h1>

<h2 id="general-information">General information</h2>

<p>This website is powered by <a href="http://middlemanapp.com">Middleman</a>.</p>

<h2 id="how-to-build-the-website">How to build the website?</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Clone the repository</li>
  <li>Change to <strong>source</strong> branch
<code>
git checkout source
</code></li>
  <li>Install all the dependencies
<code>
bundle install
</code></li>
  <li>Run the server
<code>
middleman server
</code></li>
  <li>The website is in http://localhost:4567</li>
  <li>To deploy the site:
<code>
middleman deploy
</code></li>
</ul>
